{"tid":1596772,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚惠珠：旅遊、零售和食肆 員工，是「低端服務業」人士","createTime":"2019-09-26T15:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T04:50:44.000Z","uid":226548,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"40427789053d476e45704ce315f7e493a05bdc4f","tid":1596772,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tam-21_3taQg_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftam-21_3taQg_1200x0.png&h=5d634aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最新加入的要求的是基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠，她今天指很希望立法會一開始復會後，便可討論《反蒙面法》，「第一，我認為不可蒙面可令大家知道犯法會付出代價，被通緝、被逮捕。反蒙面法在全世界很多民主先進法治國家也行之有效。」她解釋現時的不只是被打的警察，而是全個香港社會，「我們的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">旅遊、零售和食肆各方面低端服務業人士</span></strong>首先會受到影響，之後會百業蕭條。」"},{"pid":"4a3854a8e47ed77c1203aa40386f3558e67d3c5b","tid":1596772,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/譚惠珠促立法會盡快討論反蒙面法-郭榮鏗-適得其反-立會勢再被包圍/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0%E4%BF%83%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E5%8F%8D%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E9%83%AD%E6%A6%AE%E9%8F%97-%E9%81%A9%E5%BE%97%E5%85%B6%E5%8F%8D-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%8B%A2%E5%86%8D%E8%A2%AB%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%2F&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAwyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=8a235d85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0%E4%BF%83%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E5%8F%8D%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E9%83%AD%E6%A6%AE%E9%8F%97-%E9%81%A9%E5%BE%97%E5%85%B6%E5%8F%8D-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%8B%A2%E5%86%8D%E8%A2%AB%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%2F&h=c7478ef9\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/譚惠珠促立法會盡快討論反蒙面法-郭榮鏗-適得其